This app changes the Agent Interface to show the NOTE tab instead of the REPLY tab by default when viewing a ticket.

INSTALLATION
============

* Download deskpro_default_notetab.zip
* Go to Admin > Apps then click the "Upload App" button.

MODIFY
======

The source of this app is visible in the deskpro_default_notetab directory.

If you make changes and want to install your modified app, you just need to ZIP up the directory and install it in the same was as described above.